IASIS Healthcare Corp.

                    IASIS Healthcare Corp. owns and operates community-focused hospitals. It offers acute care and behavioral health hospitals in Arizona, Arkansas, Colorado, Louisiana, Texas, and Utah. The company was founded in 1998 and is headquartered in Franklin, TN.                  




