Sandra K. McRee



Ms. Sandra K. McRee is Chief Operating Officer at CareView Communications, Inc. and President at Mcree Consulting Services, Inc. She is on the Board of Directors at Professional Education Corp. and Women Business Leaders of the US Health Care Industry Fnd.
Ms. McRee was previously employed as Vice Chairman by IASIS Healthcare LLC, Regional Vice President by Province HealthCare Co., Division President by Columbia Healthcare Corp., and an Assistant Vice President by Community Health Systems, Inc. She also served on the board at IASIS Healthcare Corp.



