Sandra K. McRee  Chief Operating Officer, CareView Communications, Inc.AgeTotal Calculated CompensationThis person is connected to 0 Board Members in 0 different organizations across 3 different industries.61$331,652As of Fiscal Year 2016
Background

		Ms. Sandra K. McRee has been the Chief Operating Officer of Careview Communications, Inc. since November 1, 2013. Ms. McRee served as the Chief Operating Officer of IASIS Healthcare LLC from May 2001 to October 2010. Ms. McRee served as Chief Operating Officer of IASIS Healthcare Corporation from May 2001 to October 2010. She served as the President of IASIS Healthcare Corporation. She served as the President of IASIS Healthcare LLC since May 11, 2004. Ms. McRee has ... more than 25 years of healthcare management experience. Ms. McRee served as a Regional Vice President for Province Healthcare Corporation from April 1999 to May 2001, where she oversaw the operations of five facilities in Florida, Louisiana and Mississippi. Ms. McRee also served as Vice President, Operations of Province from October 1998 to March 1999. From August 1997 to September 1998, she served as a Division President for Columbia/HCA. Ms. McRee served as a Group Vice President, Operations for Columbia/HCA from May 1995 to July 1997. Prior to joining Columbia/HCA, Ms. McRee served as an Assistant Vice President for Community Health Systems Inc., where she oversaw 36 facilities. Ms. McRee has spent her entire professional career in the healthcare industry. She served as Non-Executive Vice Chairman of IASIS Healthcare LLC since October 2010 and served as its Vice Chairman from April 2010 to October 21, 2011. She served as Director of IASIS Healthcare LLC since April 2010.Read Full Background




